e31ae8c7beda014c34d07c616837330e03","tid":346113,"uid":51391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:44:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1 自己飲<br />\n2 下家飲<br />\n3 指人飲<br />\n4 做動作<br />\n5 圍枚<br />\n6 撞機</blockquote><br />\n有無圖 好似係呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7c48zfg2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7c48zfg2&h=0d17c259&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3461be0d7caf6986c82f8d39c36e15e80581e32","tid":346113,"uid":21306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>King's cup?</blockquote><br />\n唔係"},{"pid":"cf37a64a437abb7c4e884094f82eadd12c1a32a0","tid":346113,"uid":21306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:49:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1 自己飲<br />\n2 下家飲<br />\n3 指人飲<br />\n4 做動作<br />\n5 圍枚<br />\n6 撞機</blockquote><br />\n有無圖 好似係呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7c48zfg2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7c48zfg2&h=0d17c259&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n。。。有個係廁所牌 免死金牌"},{"pid":"e2e8364d59a0828e00a575a0c987588f1cf9285b","tid":346113,"uid":7820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:50:22.000Z","msg":"似係ring of fire?"},{"pid":"80bd0840a1e78e0fa9b8c9c1895b10d302bc9b21","tid":346113,"uid":21306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T20:15:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>似係ring of fire?</blockquote><br />\n類似但啲動作唔係"},{"pid":"79e4b85feed284538d19a3af275c916ab3107858","tid":346113,"uid":17170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T21:31:47.000Z","msg":"之前玩過類似<br />\n好似叫荷包蛋<br />\n好似8係荷包蛋 但唔記得係要用黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3e7267e6d770731e148d565f5e60e31ecb0450","tid":346113,"uid":4418,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T13:56:10.000Z","msg":"啤牌<br />\n<br />\nA指一家飲<br />\n2指兩家飲（可指同一家兩次）<br />\n3撞機<br />\n4女仔飲<br />\n5男仔飲<br />\n6鬥快用左手手指㩒枱，最慢個飲<br />\n7圍枚<br />\n8上家飲<br />\n9握手（總人數雙數時揭牌個唔使握，握唔到手個飲）<br />\n10下家飲<br />\nJ廁所牌<br />\nQ自己飲半杯<br />\nK自己飲，第一隻1/4杯，第二隻半杯，第三隻3/4杯，第四隻一杯同完game<br />\n<br />\n冇J嘅人如果想去廁所要飲一杯。另外抽咗啲牌要放自己前面，起蛇飲一杯，花兩杯，如此類推牌型越勁飲越多。當然規矩你可自定，你想起三條就要飲都得。"}]}